.SH DESCRIPTION
.sp
Calling this API causes a message to be sent to the end user with a confirmation code that is required to change the user\(aqs password. For the \fBUsername\fP parameter, you can use the username or user alias. The method used to send the confirmation code is sent according to the specified AccountRecoverySetting. For more information, see \fI\%Recovering User Accounts\fP in the \fIAmazon Cognito Developer Guide\fP . If neither a verified phone number nor a verified email exists, an \fBInvalidParameterException\fP is thrown. To use the confirmation code for resetting the password, call \fI\%ConfirmForgotPassword\fP .
.sp
See also: AWS API Documentation
.sp
See \(aqaws help\(aq for descriptions of global parameters.
